#################################################################
Read and edit makefile. Asign 'testcode' to your tests
in Makefile:
    testcode    = example_test.h

Generate your cxxtest with 

 make testcode.cpp

Test Matrix01.o with

 make runtest01

Run the test

 ./runtest01

